description: Generated frontend transport contracts are not hand-edited
globs: frontend/src/shared/api/contracts/**/*.ts
alwaysApply: false
---

# Generated Contracts

- Treat `frontend/src/shared/api/contracts/generated.ts` as generated code. Do not hand-edit it.
- If a generated type is wrong or missing, fix `backend/openapi/deadmans.v1.yaml` and regenerate instead of patching generated output.
- Keep `frontend/src/shared/api/contracts/index.ts` focused on stable aliases and intentional re-exports; do not manually mirror the full generated surface there.
- Prefer stable aliases from `index.ts` in feature code when they provide a cleaner boundary than raw generated names.
